己的诉讼中&lt;/a>;。平等就业机会委员会...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/28/23894848/tesla-lawsuit-severe-discrimination-harassment-eeoc&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip ;&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/28/23894848/tesla-lawsuit-severe-discrimination-harassment-eeoc" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/28/23894848/tesla-lawsuit-severe-discrimination-harassment-eeoc</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-09-28T16:37:44-04:00</published><updated> 2023-09-28T16:37:44-04:00</updated><title>最好的 iPhone</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;在浅蓝色条纹背景上显示 iPhone 的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/FMMd4AcCGaKxyOcDWjmM3fN__6g=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72025718/236552_Best_iPhone_for_most_people.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;像专业人士一样浏览 Apple 冗长的 iPhone 产品目录。&lt;/em>; |图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;无论您想要续航数天的电池还是最优惠的价格，我们都为您推荐了一些您会喜欢的 iPhone。&lt;/p>; &lt;p >; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23618862/best-iphone-camera-battery-screen-guide&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23618862/best-iphone-camera-battery-screen-guide" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23618862/best-iphone-camera-battery-screen-guide</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-09-28T16:15:49-04:00</published><updated> 2023-09-28T16:15:49-04:00</updated><title> 2023 年最佳娱乐</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;吉卜力工作室电影《男孩与苍鹭》中的静态图像。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/LzkJxK5kGWkthfSVQ5lQd2tOLgo=/182x0:1739x1038/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72008987/kimitachi003.27.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;男孩和苍鹭。&lt;/em>; |图片：吉卜力工作室&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p class=&quot;p--has-dropcap&quot; id=&quot;v4IULG&quo